Dialogue: 0,1:21:46.98,1:21:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,consciousness, for the achievement of enlightenment, the undoing of negative karma, all right,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:51.79,1:21:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,to get to the positive side of the balance, karmic balance, requires the undoing of negative
Dialogue: 0,1:21:56.79,1:22:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,side, which can be done in a variety of ways, some very, very specifically, almost a linear
