Dialogue: 0,1:22:24.02,1:22:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,there's no point in crying about the state of the world,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:30.79,1:22:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,a being from a different dimension has appeared, who's going to tell me the secrets of existence,
