Dialogue: 0,1:23:54.06,1:24:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,what do you think, what is about truth that you want to mystify and keep secret, control,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:06.63,1:24:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,right, control, all right, so in this lifetime, that comes back to you, and now you have a chance to say no to it,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:17.71,1:24:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,all right, so to know that everything is evolving automatically is a consequence of evolution,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:26.22,1:24:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,because evolution is how creation is expressed to the witness, it isn't what it is,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:34.11,1:24:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's what it seems to the witness, and then when you let go of the witness,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:40.09,1:24:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,you are evolution, thanks, God, you are creation, man, what did you think it was,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:49.58,1:24:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,you are the evolution of creation, you are the evolution of creation,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:56.52,1:25:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,you are how creation evolved itself, on up from the animal kingdom, on up through the spiritual
Dialogue: 0,1:25:02.60,1:25:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,dimensions, and then on into the non-linear, non-material presence, right, in that way,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:13.42,1:25:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,this returns to its source, so we'll resume the slides, you can't give a lecture without a slide,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:20.82,1:25:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,boy, give you a PhD, I say, where's your slides, you can't get a PhD without slides, nowadays it's
Dialogue: 0,1:25:35.28,1:25:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,neat, you can give them all the slides in a little box like this, you know, used to be you had to have
Dialogue: 0,1:25:40.28,1:25:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,your slide box, so that the committee could review your work, you see, all right, these are the spiritual practices,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:49.05,1:25:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,so by intention, by alignment, by supplication, and by declaration, the job for declaration,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:58.63,1:26:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,that's the time to make sure who's going to pay your bills, who's going to carry out the garbage,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:04.53,1:26:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,because by declaration, when you declare that you are a servant of Almighty God to thee, O Lord,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:12.98,1:26:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,you have just changed everything, and don't be naive and think that you haven't, you have changed
Dialogue: 0,1:26:19.96,1:26:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,it dramatically.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:22.22,1:26:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The sequence of a life events that you summon forth will unfold of a totally different dimension
Dialogue: 0,1:26:28.20,1:26:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,than people below 200, below 200, you go from imperfection to imperfection, to imperfection,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:35.32,1:26:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,to imperfection, total dissatisfaction, resentment, pity, because you see whatever condition it is,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:43.24,1:26:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,imperfection, you have desire and greed, desire and greed, I have to get it, so you go back to being a
Dialogue: 0,1:26:51.72,1:26:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,protozoa,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:52.44,1:26:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,protozoa,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:53.60,1:26:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,protozoa,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:53.82,1:26:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,protozoa,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:54.74,1:26:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,that only lives by getting,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:59.52,1:27:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,and you're refuting the divinity of your creation,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:06.04,1:27:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,that that which you are, by virtue of what it is, summons forth that which it needs from the universe,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:13.84,1:27:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,it's hard to be poor, try it, it's hard to starve to death, try it, you can't starve to death,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:30.28,1:27:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,they call the police,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:35.62,1:27:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,he hasn't eaten in a week, yeah,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:37.93,1:27:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:39.03,1:27:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I was the consultant to the Episcopal Zen Monastery,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:43.12,1:27:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,the sisterhoods and residents, Catholic, Episcopal, all that, you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:48.98,1:27:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,and they'd bring in some monk from the Zen Monastery,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:52.82,1:27:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,is he catatonic or is he in Samadhi?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:57.10,1:27:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it needs his Tuesday,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:58.86,1:28:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,is it Samadhi or Catatonia?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:07.51,1:28:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The observer can't tell,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:10.14,1:28:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,if you've been there, you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:12.64,1:28:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,the way through,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:13.48,1:28:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,but,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:14.34,1:28:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,if you haven't been there,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:16.41,1:28:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,you give him Thorazine and Shakti,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:17.85,1:28:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,so in one of the books, anyway, I delineated how to differentiate,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:25.39,1:28:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,and of course, with calibrated levels of consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:28.63,1:28:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,you can get right away with, is this a schizophrenic break,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:32.29,1:28:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,or is this a guy in Samadhi, you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:34.35,1:28:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,because it doesn't happen with such frequency,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:38.59,1:28:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,and Catatonia is quite impressive,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:42.04,1:28:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'll tell you a story about Catatonia,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:43.64,1:28:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I was,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:44.68,1:28:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,in the state hospital, right into the psychiatric hospital,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:48.15,1:28:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,and we had a catatonic,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:51.42,1:28:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,catatonic, and he was a tall skinny thing,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:54.52,1:28:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,and he wouldn't eat, so we tube fed him,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:56.34,1:28:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, once a day, you got a tube down there,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:59.16,1:29:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,but he would, in Catatonia, the person has,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:02.64,1:29:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,what do they call it, cataplexy or something like that, anyway,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:06.86,1:29:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,if you put his arm like this, he will leave it there,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:09.68,1:29:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,you can come back three days from now, it's still there,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:12.82,1:29:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,immobile,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:14.24,1:29:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,so we had a catatonic on the ward,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:16.82,1:29:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,and I had the tube for these guys every morning,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:19.70,1:29:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,make sure the tube went down the esophagus and not the bronchi,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:23.52,1:29:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,so, yeah, so the doctor had to come around and place the tube,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:27.68,1:29:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and then the nurse could take it from there,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:29.02,1:29:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,but, so you don't get the enriched milk in their lung,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:34.39,1:29:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,and kill them,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:36.01,1:29:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I used to feel sorry for these creatures,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:39.00,1:29:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,because they didn't want to eat, they couldn't eat,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:40.98,1:29:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,and tears would come to their eyes,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:42.28,1:29:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,but there wasn't anything I could do,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:43.34,1:29:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,the law said you got to see to it they stay alive,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:45.46,1:29:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,all right, so we had this catatonic,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:49.08,1:29:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,and,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:49.90,1:29:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,at the hospital, we had the doctor,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:52.74,1:29:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,the doctor was a short little guy with a bald,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:56.84,1:29:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:58.04,1:29:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I forgot his name now,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:59.10,1:30:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,remember his name, yeah, anyway,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:02.54,1:30:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,and anyway, we had a head nurse, just got off,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:05.58,1:30:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,the boat from Ireland,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:06.92,1:30:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,and this was in Ward's Island, underneath the Chiropractic Bridge,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:09.78,1:30:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,the old Manhattan State Hospital,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:12.29,1:30:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,and the personnel were mainly immigrants from Ireland, so,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:17.37,1:30:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,yeah, Nellie Murphy, so Nellie Murphy was about 6'2",
Dialogue: 0,1:30:20.63,1:30:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and all brawn,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:22.72,1:30:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,and doctor, whatever his name is, I forget, it was about this high,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:26.54,1:30:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,well, the nurses weren't supposed to smoke or drink coffee in the nursing office,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:30.82,1:30:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,and so this catatonic, you put them up against the wall,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:35.30,1:30:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,and they tube feed them, and then you put them up against the wall,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:37.98,1:30:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,and somebody just for something else to do,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:39.60,1:30:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,would put his hand like this, you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:46.73,1:30:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,well, you try and kid them out of it,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:47.99,1:30:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,you go by, you put your hat on it,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:52.82,1:30:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,you salute it,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:54.89,1:30:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,pretend you're going to bite it,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:56.21,1:30:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,no response,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:56.61,1:30:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,no response,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:59.62,1:31:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,he was this way for years.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:01.99,1:31:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,One day, Nellie Murphy and Travis, that was it,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:07.73,1:31:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,one day, Dr. Travis and Nellie,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:09.99,1:31:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,come walking down, because they were separate buildings,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:12.93,1:31:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,it looked like Wuthering Heights or something, you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:15.03,1:31:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,late 1800s, all these,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:18.01,1:31:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,brick buildings slightly tipped over the years,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:21.25,1:31:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,and the floor is a little crooked,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:22.89,1:31:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,and the smell of about 150 years of urine is coming up,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:28.75,1:31:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,anyway, Nellie and Travis come walking down the walk, you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:34.57,1:31:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,and this catatonic, it's sawed out the window,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:38.41,1:31:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,he hadn't spoken in 20 years,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:39.77,1:31:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and all of a sudden he says,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:42.32,1:31:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Travis and Murphy,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:45.64,1:31:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,and the nurses quickly put away their cigarettes and coffee,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:48.24,1:31:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and opened the windows,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:49.36,1:31:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,and he never said anything again.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:58.80,1:31:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, we'll resume.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:02.63,1:32:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,So how do you tell that condition from Samadhi, you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:05.63,1:32:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,and in the meditative states, you get into high states,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:10.74,1:32:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,but then when you open your eyes,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:12.60,1:32:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,the state disappears,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:14.22,1:32:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,or if it still maintains with eyes open,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:17.64,1:32:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,it disappears when you begin to stand up and walk around,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:21.26,1:32:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and you can't participate in the world,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:25.42,1:32:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,so, because at a certain level,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:30.50,1:32:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,the capacity, actually, as the state evolves,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:35.32,1:32:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,and that's why I warned you about it,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:36.46,1:32:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,you hit a point in which,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:37.98,1:32:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,the capacity to function is zero.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:40.96,1:32:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,There isn't capacity to function.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:43.12,1:32:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,First of all, there isn't anybody to function,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:46.73,1:32:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,nor is there anything to function about.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:50.67,1:32:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That's hard to explain,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:51.89,1:32:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,but at 600, you become what's called a mystic,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:55.65,1:33:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,and the world may have reasons for this body to go on walking around,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:00.79,1:33:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,but the body itself has no such interest, you see.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:04.06,1:33:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, whatever happens is of karmic propensity,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:07.82,1:33:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,a karmic propensity,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:09.64,1:33:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:09.84,1:33:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,and if the karma is such,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:13.52,1:33:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,then the continuation will continue,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:16.52,1:33:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,and if the karma is already fulfilled,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:18.68,1:33:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and there is no obligation or commitment
Dialogue: 0,1:33:21.42,1:33:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,before you have reentered this lifetime,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:26.62,1:33:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,then you may just topple over.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:28.08,1:33:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,So, to refunction again requires
Dialogue: 0,1:33:37.66,1:33:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,the recreation of what you would call,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:40.77,1:33:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,it's not recreated,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:41.87,1:33:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,the activation of a potentiality,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:44.13,1:33:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,it's not something called the personage.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:47.57,1:33:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a functionality,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:49.57,1:33:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,it's not a thing or an entity.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:52.76,1:33:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So, the capacity to,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:54.76,1:33:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,let's say, explain to an audience what goes on,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:58.99,1:34:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,does so via a quality of the personage.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:02.99,1:34:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,So, if the destiny is to continue on in the body,
Dialogue: 0,1:34:05.99,1:34:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,let's say to teach for some reason,
Dialogue: 0,1:34:07.99,1:34:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,teach or something,
Dialogue: 0,1:34:08.99,1:34:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,then the capacity for personizing the knowingness,
Dialogue: 0,1:34:15.66,1:34:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,emerges as vocabularization, et cetera,
Dialogue: 0,1:34:22.23,1:34:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,of which one is not the participant.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:25.90,1:34:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,They have no idea what's going to be said next at all.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:29.86,1:34:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why it's great.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:32.86,1:34:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Never heard it before.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:34.86,1:34:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,So, there may or may not be
Dialogue: 0,1:34:40.70,1:34:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,the emergence of a person,
Dialogue: 0,1:34:43.70,1:34:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,a personalization.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:46.12,1:34:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like an aspect of the experiencer
Dialogue: 0,1:34:49.12,1:34:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,that by karmic control,
Dialogue: 0,1:34:55.32,1:34:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,by contract almost,
Dialogue: 0,1:34:57.32,1:34:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,by agreement,
Dialogue: 0,1:34:58.32,1:35:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,it continues on to fulfill a function.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:01.32,1:35:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not the function,
Dialogue: 0,1:35:02.32,1:35:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,nor is there any person to do the function.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:05.38,1:35:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The function is its own self.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:08.38,1:35:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The function functions
Dialogue: 0,1:35:10.38,1:35:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,without any person behind the function,
Dialogue: 0,1:35:13.38,1:35:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,without any purpose or direction,
Dialogue: 0,1:35:15.38,1:35:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,because it's part of evolution.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:18.38,1:35:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,So, those that are destined to become enlightened, then,
Dialogue: 0,1:35:22.77,1:35:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,express the potentiality
Dialogue: 0,1:35:26.15,1:35:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,of creation and evolution
Dialogue: 0,1:35:29.15,1:35:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,returning to its source,
Dialogue: 0,1:35:31.15,1:35:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,and that's what the world calls enlightenment.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:34.15,1:35:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, enlightenment, at least from this realm.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:37.31,1:35:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,From other realms, it's called kindergarten.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:47.74,1:35:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,See, I'm a trainee for kindergarten.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:51.15,1:35:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:53.37,1:35:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,These various spiritual practices.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:56.46,1:35:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, so once you've made the commitment,
Dialogue: 0,1:35:59.46,1:36:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,the reason you made the commitment
Dialogue: 0,1:36:01.46,1:36:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,was because you're merely stating what you've already,
Dialogue: 0,1:36:07.46,1:36:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,what your future is,
Dialogue: 0,1:36:09.19,1:36:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,to become enlightened.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:10.19,1:36:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody else is here.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:12.19,1:36:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Only golfers are at a class on how to golf,
Dialogue: 0,1:36:14.19,1:36:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,you know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:17.51,1:36:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would you be in a class on golf?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:20.51,1:36:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So, only because one has already chosen that
Dialogue: 0,1:36:24.51,1:36:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,is, that is your destiny.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:27.51,1:36:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, one is,
Dialogue: 0,1:36:30.58,1:36:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,the appropriate way to be with that destiny
Dialogue: 0,1:36:34.57,1:36:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,is one of respect.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:36.57,1:36:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Respect yourself.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:38.89,1:36:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Respect the information.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:40.89,1:36:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Respect the inspiration.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:43.89,1:36:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Because if that is your destiny,
Dialogue: 0,1:36:49.32,1:36:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,that certainly deserves respect.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:52.32,1:36:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Respect yourself.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:54.54,1:36:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Respect truth.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:55.54,1:36:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't deviate it.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:58.82,1:37:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,To not deviate out of guilt
Dialogue: 0,1:37:02.07,1:37:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,is to just join the ego.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:04.07,1:37:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you don't deviate.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:06.07,1:37:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Respect truth out of your own integrity.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:10.07,1:37:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, what is due a teacher?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:13.20,1:37:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Respect.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:14.20,1:37:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:15.30,1:37:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Not worship.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:16.30,1:37:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Not glorification.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:19.83,1:37:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would the absolute truth
Dialogue: 0,1:37:22.50,1:37:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and the infinite glory of God
Dialogue: 0,1:37:23.50,1:37:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,need glorification
Dialogue: 0,1:37:25.50,1:37:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,or amplification?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:27.50,1:37:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's already so stunningly overwhelming what it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:31.50,1:37:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Any two cents you can add is actually a detraction.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:38.33,1:37:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:40.77,1:37:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,One of the things that are done then
Dialogue: 0,1:37:42.77,1:37:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,to reinforce the commitment,
Dialogue: 0,1:37:44.86,1:37:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,and I think they're quite interesting,
Dialogue: 0,1:37:46.86,1:37:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,just the sound, om,
Dialogue: 0,1:37:48.86,1:37:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,which we're going to do this afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:51.18,1:37:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,When do we do om?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:53.25,1:37:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,After lunch?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:54.25,1:37:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's morning now, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:56.25,1:37:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,When do we do om?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:58.70,1:37:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The chant?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:59.70,1:38:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:02.23,1:38:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,This afternoon?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:04.39,1:38:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's morning now.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:05.39,1:38:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:06.39,1:38:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:07.58,1:38:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So we do om,
Dialogue: 0,1:38:08.58,1:38:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,which we're going to do collectively.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:11.81,1:38:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Then there's the various variations.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:13.81,1:38:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:14.81,1:38:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Various variations of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:17.54,1:38:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You see that all these things
Dialogue: 0,1:38:19.54,1:38:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,subserve spiritual intention.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:23.50,1:38:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,This is over 200.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:25.92,1:38:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,These are over 200.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:26.92,1:38:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,This is already 540.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:28.92,1:38:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,One way to reach an advanced state
Dialogue: 0,1:38:32.14,1:38:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,is to drink yourself to death.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:39.93,1:38:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,See if you can kill yourself with booze,
Dialogue: 0,1:38:42.93,1:38:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,bad women and drugs,
Dialogue: 0,1:38:44.93,1:38:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,all at the same time
Dialogue: 0,1:38:47.28,1:38:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,while you gamble away your last few dollars.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:49.28,1:38:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And you either get to this way
Dialogue: 0,1:38:51.86,1:38:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,or you leave.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:52.86,1:38:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Well,
Dialogue: 0,1:38:55.68,1:38:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,through that lifetime,
Dialogue: 0,1:38:56.68,1:38:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,a lot of people went out
Dialogue: 0,1:38:57.68,1:38:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,five or six times
Dialogue: 0,1:38:59.68,1:39:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,due to addiction
Dialogue: 0,1:39:00.68,1:39:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,and it's only the sixth lifetime
Dialogue: 0,1:39:02.68,1:39:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,that they finally got sober.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:04.68,1:39:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,So it ain't all that easy
Dialogue: 0,1:39:06.68,1:39:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,because that brings you right up at 540.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:08.68,1:39:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,540 is 0.4% of the human population.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:13.68,1:39:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,0.4% of the population
Dialogue: 0,1:39:16.94,1:39:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,ever gets to 540.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:19.94,1:39:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So we don't have to feel bad.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:21.48,1:39:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Well,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:22.48,1:39:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,we don't have to feel sorry
Dialogue: 0,1:39:23.48,1:39:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,for these people anymore.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:26.48,1:39:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The thing is,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:27.48,1:39:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,they're way ahead of us already.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:31.86,1:39:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Poor elkies.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:32.86,1:39:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, right.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:33.86,1:39:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,At 540,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:35.86,1:39:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,at 540,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:36.86,1:39:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,they're in a state
Dialogue: 0,1:39:37.86,1:39:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,that you wish you could experience.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:41.18,1:39:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:42.18,1:39:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So we,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:43.98,1:39:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,the golden rule
Dialogue: 0,1:39:44.98,1:39:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,doesn't make any point below 200,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:46.98,1:39:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,as we said this morning.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:47.98,1:39:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,To give a person an honest measure
Dialogue: 0,1:39:51.72,1:39:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,is stupid in certain cultures.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:53.72,1:39:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:54.72,1:39:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only over 200
Dialogue: 0,1:39:55.72,1:39:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,that it gains any validity.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:57.72,1:40:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It is the various things we do,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:00.42,1:40:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,the various prayers,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:01.42,1:40:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,walking the maze.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:03.42,1:40:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,When we were in Chartres Cathedral,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:05.71,1:40:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,they were very clever there.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:07.71,1:40:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,They won't allow you to walk the maze.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:08.71,1:40:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,They cleverly do that
Dialogue: 0,1:40:09.71,1:40:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,by putting chairs all over
Dialogue: 0,1:40:10.71,1:40:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,so you can't walk the maze.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:13.71,1:40:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess they'd have
Dialogue: 0,1:40:14.71,1:40:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,an endless parade of people
Dialogue: 0,1:40:15.71,1:40:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,lined up outside
Dialogue: 0,1:40:16.71,1:40:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,all walking the maze.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:18.71,1:40:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't see what's wrong with that.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:22.06,1:40:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,If I were in the cathedral,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:23.16,1:40:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd have maze.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:24.16,1:40:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You go in there,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:25.16,1:40:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,you do the maze.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:26.16,1:40:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,In,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:27.16,1:40:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,out.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:28.16,1:40:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:29.42,1:40:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Except in the middle,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:30.58,1:40:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,you want to go to the bathroom,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:31.58,1:40:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,you gotta,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:32.58,1:40:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:33.58,1:40:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:36.34,1:40:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't have done it that way,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:37.34,1:40:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,but I don't know
Dialogue: 0,1:40:38.34,1:40:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,their administrative problems.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:40.34,1:40:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,They have a thing in the front for money.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:42.41,1:40:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,They hit you with that right away.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:45.02,1:40:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Walking in Chartres Cathedral,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:46.02,1:40:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,money.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:47.02,1:40:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The next thing you get
Dialogue: 0,1:40:48.50,1:40:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,is everybody's on their cell phone.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:50.50,1:40:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's the most incredible.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:52.85,1:40:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It calibrates over 700.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:54.85,1:40:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:56.17,1:40:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,it's stupendous.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:58.17,1:40:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You can see that many workmen
Dialogue: 0,1:40:59.17,1:41:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,gave an entire lifetime
Dialogue: 0,1:41:01.17,1:41:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,surrendering it to God
Dialogue: 0,1:41:03.33,1:41:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,as the perfection of their work,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:05.33,1:41:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,the Karma Yoga of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:08.68,1:41:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,People are on their cell phones.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:10.68,1:41:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's unbelievable.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:12.78,1:41:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,They're on their cell phones.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:14.78,1:41:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, God.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:15.78,1:41:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, well.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:18.35,1:41:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You either get it
Dialogue: 0,1:41:19.35,1:41:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,or you don't get it,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:20.35,1:41:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:24.18,1:41:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like seeing God
Dialogue: 0,1:41:25.18,1:41:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,and saying,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:26.18,1:41:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,golly whiz, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:28.54,1:41:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Things become,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:31.63,1:41:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,you see how 540
Dialogue: 0,1:41:34.24,1:41:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,is the result of intention.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:36.24,1:41:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,By devotion and commitment to God
Dialogue: 0,1:41:38.69,1:41:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,does the Ganges become holy.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:42.42,1:41:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:43.42,1:41:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,many of these things
Dialogue: 0,1:41:44.42,1:41:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,because they come
Dialogue: 0,1:41:45.42,1:41:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,from different cultures,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:46.42,1:41:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,instead of ridiculing them,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:47.42,1:41:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,you see that
Dialogue: 0,1:41:48.42,1:41:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,turning a prayer wheel
Dialogue: 0,1:41:50.94,1:41:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,by intention
Dialogue: 0,1:41:51.94,1:41:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and
Dialogue: 0,1:41:53.26,1:41:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,like genuflection,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:55.26,1:41:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,kneeling to pray,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:57.80,1:42:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,put one's hands together like this
Dialogue: 0,1:42:00.12,1:42:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,is an act of respect.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:01.12,1:42:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,For God,
Dialogue: 0,1:42:02.12,1:42:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,for a teacher,
Dialogue: 0,1:42:03.12,1:42:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,for truth,
Dialogue: 0,1:42:04.12,1:42:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,for a divine place.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:06.12,1:42:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Prayerful handcrafts,
Dialogue: 0,1:42:07.25,1:42:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,devotional acts,
Dialogue: 0,1:42:08.25,1:42:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,turning the prayer wheel,
Dialogue: 0,1:42:09.25,1:42:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,burning of incense,
Dialogue: 0,1:42:10.25,1:42:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,the wailing wall,
Dialogue: 0,1:42:11.25,1:42:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,bathing in the Ganges,
Dialogue: 0,1:42:12.25,1:42:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,the prayer of St. Francis of Assisi.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:14.25,1:42:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's a different level.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:16.25,1:42:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:17.25,1:42:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,To be a channel of thy will,
Dialogue: 0,1:42:18.25,1:42:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,oh Lord.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:19.25,1:42:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll go to the next.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:20.38,1:42:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:21.38,1:42:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So here is the left brain below 200.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:34.13,1:42:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the animal evolution
Dialogue: 0,1:42:43.23,1:42:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,up to consciousness level 200.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:45.55,1:42:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,So,
Dialogue: 0,1:42:46.55,1:42:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,the animal evolution
Dialogue: 0,1:42:47.55,1:42:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,up to consciousness level 200.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:48.55,1:42:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It's emotional primarily
Dialogue: 0,1:42:54.47,1:42:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,and it has to do with survival.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:56.47,1:42:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It has to do with the core of the ego.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:58.47,1:42:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So,
Dialogue: 0,1:42:59.57,1:43:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,the reason ego
Dialogue: 0,1:43:00.57,1:43:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,is the way he is
Dialogue: 0,1:43:02.57,1:43:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,is because he's programmed for survival.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:05.60,1:43:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to take a piece of candy from him,
Dialogue: 0,1:43:09.88,1:43:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,he will bite you
Dialogue: 0,1:43:11.88,1:43:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,because he's supposed to.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:15.03,1:43:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore,
Dialogue: 0,1:43:16.03,1:43:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,we respect the ego
Dialogue: 0,1:43:17.67,1:43:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,rather than vilify it.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:19.67,1:43:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore,
Dialogue: 0,1:43:20.77,1:43:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,my disagreement
Dialogue: 0,1:43:21.77,1:43:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,with the textbook
Dialogue: 0,1:43:22.77,1:43:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,of the Course in Miracles
Dialogue: 0,1:43:24.77,1:43:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,is it seems to have a different energy
Dialogue: 0,1:43:26.77,1:43:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,than the workbook
Dialogue: 0,1:43:28.77,1:43:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,because it now gets into a dualistic positionality
Dialogue: 0,1:43:32.66,1:43:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,about the ego.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:33.66,1:43:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The ego is innocent
Dialogue: 0,1:43:36.43,1:43:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,by virtue of
Dialogue: 0,1:43:38.43,1:43:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,the fact that it's being
Dialogue: 0,1:43:40.94,1:43:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,what it was created to be.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:42.94,1:43:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,For humans to be here,
Dialogue: 0,1:43:45.97,1:43:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,evolution had to proceed up through the animal kingdom
Dialogue: 0,1:43:49.99,1:43:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,to finally the development of a suitable
Dialogue: 0,1:43:54.06,1:43:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,vehicle
Dialogue: 0,1:43:55.89,1:43:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,for higher consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:56.89,1:43:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,For higher consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,1:43:59.21,1:44:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,which we call human.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:00.21,1:44:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So,
Dialogue: 0,1:44:01.72,1:44:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,the only reason we're here
Dialogue: 0,1:44:03.72,1:44:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,is because of our animal.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:04.72,1:44:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So,
Dialogue: 0,1:44:06.36,1:44:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,therefore,
Dialogue: 0,1:44:07.36,1:44:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,we're grateful for our animal
Dialogue: 0,1:44:09.55,1:44:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,and I say,
Dialogue: 0,1:44:10.55,1:44:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,ego baby,
Dialogue: 0,1:44:11.55,1:44:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,if it wasn't for you,
Dialogue: 0,1:44:12.55,1:44:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't be standing up
Dialogue: 0,1:44:13.55,1:44:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,walking around
Dialogue: 0,1:44:15.10,1:44:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,without the animal.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:17.10,1:44:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,We wouldn't have a physicality
Dialogue: 0,1:44:20.10,1:44:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,to walk around in.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:22.67,1:44:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Then this physicality reaches
Dialogue: 0,1:44:25.38,1:44:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,a certain point of evolution,
Dialogue: 0,1:44:27.38,1:44:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,but it has an even higher potentiality
Dialogue: 0,1:44:29.38,1:44:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,than just the animal.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:30.38,1:44:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And at 200,
Dialogue: 0,1:44:35.22,1:44:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,the energy of creation,
Dialogue: 0,1:44:36.22,1:44:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,1:44:37.22,1:44:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,the light of God,
Dialogue: 0,1:44:38.22,1:44:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,then,
Dialogue: 0,1:44:39.22,1:44:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,manifests
Dialogue: 0,1:44:40.26,1:44:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and we begin to experience
Dialogue: 0,1:44:42.26,1:44:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,the flow of the Kundalini energy
Dialogue: 0,1:44:44.26,1:44:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and now the brain switches
Dialogue: 0,1:44:46.26,1:44:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and processes information differently.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:49.26,1:44:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It experiences the world as more benign
Dialogue: 0,1:44:52.32,1:44:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,and its intention is different.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:57.47,1:44:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,And one of the main reasons
Dialogue: 0,1:44:59.95,1:45:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,is because at consciousness level 200,
Dialogue: 0,1:45:02.95,1:45:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,you develop an etheric brain.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:06.08,1:45:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The etheric brain.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:07.08,1:45:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The etheric brain.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:09.18,1:45:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Prior to 200,
Dialogue: 0,1:45:11.59,1:45:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,people and animals
Dialogue: 0,1:45:14.04,1:45:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,don't have a personal karma,
Dialogue: 0,1:45:17.26,1:45:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,they have a group karma.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:19.26,1:45:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,They're controlled by an attractor field.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:22.26,1:45:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The attractor field draws all
Dialogue: 0,1:45:25.36,1:45:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,like unto like.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:28.36,1:45:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,At 200,
Dialogue: 0,1:45:30.58,1:45:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,you now have choice.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:32.58,1:45:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You experience and realize
Dialogue: 0,1:45:34.80,1:45:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,that you are
Dialogue: 0,1:45:35.80,1:45:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,and this are is now responsible
Dialogue: 0,1:45:38.86,1:45:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,and capable of choice.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:42.34,1:45:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Culpability also increases at 200.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:46.34,1:45:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:48.34,1:45:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Also culpability.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:51.27,1:45:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that you know that you are
Dialogue: 0,1:45:53.27,1:45:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,and others know that they are,
Dialogue: 0,1:45:55.27,1:45:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,now the consequences karmically
Dialogue: 0,1:45:58.27,1:45:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,become different.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:59.27,1:46:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The karmic consequences
Dialogue: 0,1:46:01.91,1:46:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,of an animal eating a rabbit
Dialogue: 0,1:46:04.91,1:46:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,is quite different
Dialogue: 0,1:46:06.91,1:46:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,than you're taking a human life,
Dialogue: 0,1:46:07.91,1:46:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,let's say.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:08.91,1:46:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:09.91,1:46:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,So here karma changes.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:11.91,1:46:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The responsibility changes.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:13.91,1:46:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You have the inflow of Kundalini energy.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:16.91,1:46:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So we said below 200,
Dialogue: 0,1:46:19.04,1:46:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,your left brain linear,
Dialogue: 0,1:46:21.04,1:46:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,fight or flight,
Dialogue: 0,1:46:22.04,1:46:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,alarm, resistance,
Dialogue: 0,1:46:23.04,1:46:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,exhaustion,
Dialogue: 0,1:46:24.04,1:46:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,stress and the thymus,
Dialogue: 0,1:46:26.04,1:46:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,disruption of the acupuncture meridians,
Dialogue: 0,1:46:28.04,1:46:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,more prone to illness.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:30.04,1:46:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Neurotransmitter depletion
Dialogue: 0,1:46:32.33,1:46:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,is one of serotonin.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:34.33,1:46:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:35.49,1:46:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you switch the spheres,
Dialogue: 0,1:46:37.49,1:46:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,you get a different dominance.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:38.49,1:46:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nonlinear.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:40.49,1:46:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You're more interested in peace,
Dialogue: 0,1:46:41.49,1:46:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,positive emotions.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:43.49,1:46:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Immunity increases.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:45.10,1:46:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Healing increases.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:47.10,1:46:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The acupuncture system is balanced.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:50.61,1:46:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And the track to the emotions
Dialogue: 0,1:46:52.06,1:46:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,is slower than the prefrontal
Dialogue: 0,1:46:54.06,1:46:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and the etheric brain.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:57.06,1:46:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,All this is crucial.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:59.34,1:47:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And most of the world
Dialogue: 0,1:47:00.86,1:47:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,doesn't know about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:01.86,1:47:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,So we'll go to the next.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:03.95,1:47:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,We go to the next.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:13.03,1:47:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,We said that
Dialogue: 0,1:47:15.03,1:47:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,if it's not a world of cause and effect,
Dialogue: 0,1:47:17.48,1:47:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,it's a world of
Dialogue: 0,1:47:19.48,1:47:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,that which you are
Dialogue: 0,1:47:20.48,1:47:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,draws like, draws to like.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:23.54,1:47:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That which you are by your own choice then.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:26.54,1:47:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So if we look at the level of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,1:47:29.58,1:47:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,correlated with the various phenomena
Dialogue: 0,1:47:33.58,1:47:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,about which sociologists are concerned,
Dialogue: 0,1:47:36.61,1:47:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,you see, you don't see cause and effect.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:40.67,1:47:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't see cause and effect.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:42.74,1:47:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You see concordance.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:45.44,1:47:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I realized that,
Dialogue: 0,1:47:47.75,1:47:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember in World War II in the Navy.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:51.04,1:47:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,After paydays,
Dialogue: 0,1:47:52.04,1:47:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,the same guys were always broke every Friday.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:55.04,1:47:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Same guys.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:56.94,1:48:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Always broke.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:01.82,1:48:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And I learned how to make money shooting craps.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:07.82,1:48:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you why you can't win at the casino.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:11.33,1:48:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,If you look at the statistics,
Dialogue: 0,1:48:13.33,1:48:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,if you look at shooting craps,
Dialogue: 0,1:48:15.33,1:48:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll see that winning and losing,
Dialogue: 0,1:48:19.58,1:48:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,if you chart winning and losing in roulette,
Dialogue: 0,1:48:21.58,1:48:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,or craps I think,
Dialogue: 0,1:48:22.58,1:48:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,you see it spikes up,
Dialogue: 0,1:48:24.58,1:48:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,then it spikes down.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:25.58,1:48:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,These are your winnings,
Dialogue: 0,1:48:27.58,1:48:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,these are your losses.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:28.58,1:48:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,These are your winnings,
Dialogue: 0,1:48:29.58,1:48:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,these are your losses.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:31.68,1:48:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,How far of a loss can you take
Dialogue: 0,1:48:33.68,1:48:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,before you're out of the game?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:36.13,1:48:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I discovered that when I was 17.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:38.99,1:48:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to shoot craps? Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:40.99,1:48:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,How much you got on you?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:41.99,1:48:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Three bucks.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:42.99,1:48:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I got ten.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:43.99,1:48:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go for them.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:45.54,1:48:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I'm going to get his three.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:47.54,1:48:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,If I got ten.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:49.24,1:48:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You got it?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:50.24,1:48:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:51.66,1:48:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,So the house,
Dialogue: 0,1:48:52.66,1:48:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,the house,
Dialogue: 0,1:48:53.66,1:48:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,the house can go way, way down there.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:56.66,1:48:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're going to get wiped out.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:59.07,1:49:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The house can afford, you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:49:01.07,1:49:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,being five million behind.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:03.07,1:49:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:04.17,1:49:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:05.17,1:49:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,So we just go on probability,
Dialogue: 0,1:49:07.17,1:49:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,sooner or later,
Dialogue: 0,1:49:08.17,1:49:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,you're a big wheeler,
Dialogue: 0,1:49:09.17,1:49:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,a big roller,
Dialogue: 0,1:49:10.17,1:49:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,you got 40,000.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:12.17,1:49:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,40,000 is to a big house.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:15.71,1:49:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean,
Dialogue: 0,1:49:16.71,1:49:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,they eat that for lunch.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:17.71,1:49:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you go 100,000?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:19.71,1:49:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you go 200,000?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:21.71,1:49:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have to send anybody even out
Dialogue: 0,1:49:24.10,1:49:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,for extra money
Dialogue: 0,1:49:25.10,1:49:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,unless you get well over a million.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:27.10,1:49:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you go a million?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:28.10,1:49:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you can't go.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:30.10,1:49:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So you can see,
Dialogue: 0,1:49:31.10,1:49:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,obviously,
Dialogue: 0,1:49:32.10,1:49:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,it's only a matter of time.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:34.10,1:49:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to get wiped out
Dialogue: 0,1:49:35.10,1:49:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,by the downside.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:36.10,1:49:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:37.16,1:49:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Never shoot craps
Dialogue: 0,1:49:38.16,1:49:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,unless you got a lot more money
Dialogue: 0,1:49:39.16,1:49:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,than the other guy.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:42.45,1:49:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you know why your ten of the legs are right.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:49.67,1:49:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because these guys here
Dialogue: 0,1:49:51.86,1:49:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,always lose.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:53.86,1:49:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,They always lose.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:56.41,1:49:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Happiness is practically zero.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:58.41,1:50:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,And criminality is an endemic way of life.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:02.41,1:50:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an endemic way of life, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:05.92,1:50:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,They receive it as criminal.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:07.92,1:50:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You practically never hear
Dialogue: 0,1:50:09.72,1:50:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,of a child molestation,
Dialogue: 0,1:50:11.72,1:50:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,murder, kidnapping
Dialogue: 0,1:50:12.72,1:50:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,as a single isolated crime.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:15.72,1:50:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Just don't happen.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:16.72,1:50:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You know,
